metadata.name: Ketiwa
metadata.description:
Ketiwa means 'Eagle' in Sauk. 

When I wrote this song, I imagined the emotional state of a Ketiwa and visualized the kind of freedom it has to roam the skies.  I was inspired by its spirit and what it symbolizes. 

This audio offering is my way of preserving my native tongue and your support helps keep native music, art, and language alive.
